<u>NAME</u>
<b>A Timelapse Doodle</b>

<u>SYNOPSIS</u>
<b><iframe src="https://ia800200.us.archive.org/4/items/ATimelapseDoodle/atimelapsedoodle-jan-2011.ogv" frameborder="0"></iframe>
</b>

<u>DESCRIPTION</u>
<b><p>A little doodle inspired by <a href="http://rasterweb.net/raster/tag/tlbot/">Raster's creations with Timelapse Bot</a> and the 12/18/2010 Distributed Hacker Maker Network meeting where I made an impromptu claymation from stills taken of the meeting.
</b>

<b>While drawing has never really been an interest of mine, drawing in-real-life frames for animation is pretty fun.
</b>

<b>Used in the making:
</b>

<b>
<ul>
<li>Canon Powershot A550 (nothing fancy)</li>
<li>Whiteboard/dry erase marker</li>
<li>Fedora 14 Linux and ffmpeg2theora for exporting to the free and open Ogg/Theora format</a></li>
</ul>
</b>
